<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />Break their teeth in their mouths, God;</para>

<para style="q1">break out the great teeth of the young lions, Yahweh.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />Let them melt away as water that runs off;</para>

<para style="q1">when they shoot their arrows, let them be as though they had no points.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />Let them be like a snail that melts and passes away,</para>

<para style="q1">like the untimely-born child of a woman that never sees the sunlight.</para>
